<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1414] Service ranking is only obeyed on first component activation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1414</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-950&quot; title=&quot;service.ranking property not respected for singular service reference&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FELIX-950&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FELIX-950&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (released with scr 1.0.8) and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1213&quot; title=&quot;service.ranking property not respected for singular statically bound service reference&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FELIX-1213&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FELIX-1213&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (not released yet) unary services bindings are replaced if a new service is registered with a higher service ranking than the already bound service.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has been clarified in the OSGi dev list thread &quot;Questions on DS Spec&quot; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; that a service once bound is only replaced if it ceaces to be a target either by the service being unregistered of the target filter not matching any longer. Service ranking is only obeyed upon first binding of a service to the component.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To fix we have to revert the fixes for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-950&quot; title=&quot;service.ranking property not respected for singular service reference&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FELIX-950&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FELIX-950&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1213&quot; title=&quot;service.ranking property not respected for singular statically bound service reference&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FELIX-1213&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FELIX-1213&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mail-archive.com/osgi-dev@mail.osgi.org/msg00883.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.mail-archive.com/osgi-dev@mail.osgi.org/msg00883.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
